• Sign up page: log in  email/username & password - may be linked via already existing social media platform
• User Profiles: Users can create and manage their profiles.
• Public & Private Settings: both for the users profile itself  & any art work they have created,
• Art Journal Pages: Users can create, edit, and delete journal pages.
• Demographic: artists (digital)  and other
• Sharing: Users can share their journal 'pages' in a news feed.
• Calendar/Diary View: Journal pages are stored and viewable in a calendar or diary format.
• Comments and Likes: Users can comment on and like shared pages.
Notifications: Users receive notifications for comments, likes, and new shares.
